'''巴提斯·謝侯'''（{{lang-fr|'''Patrice Chéreau'''}}，{{bd|1944年|11月2日|2013年|10月7日|catIdx=Chéreau}}），法國歌劇、劇場、電影導演與電影演員。他曾以《{{link-en|親密關係 (2001年電影)|Intimacy (film)|親密關係}}》於[[柏林影展|第51屆柏林影展]]獲得[[金熊獎|金熊獎]]。

== 生平 ==
巴提斯·謝侯的父親是畫家，母親是平面設計師，他出生於[[莱济涅|莱济涅]]出生，於[[巴黎|巴黎]]求學，他因參觀[[羅浮宮|羅浮宮]]而開始對藝術感到興趣；12歲時，他就開始為話劇做舞台設計<ref name= "Independent">{{cite news | last = Kirkup | first = James | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/obituaries/patrice-chreau-film-theatre-and-opera-director-hailed-for-his-bayreuth-ring-cycle-and-for-la-reine-margot-8867348.html | title = Patrice Chéreau: Film, theatre and opera director hailed for his Bayreuth ''Ring Cycle'' and for ''La Reine Margot'' | newspaper = [[The_Independent|The Independent]] | location = London | date = 9 October 2013 | accessdate = 11 October 2013 | archive-date = 2015-09-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925115154/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/obituaries/patrice-chreau-film-theatre-and-opera-director-hailed-for-his-bayreuth-ring-cycle-and-for-la-reine-margot-8867348.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，在就讀[[路易大帝中學|路易大帝中學]]時，他即因在學校劇場擔任導演、演員而廣受巴黎劇評人熟知。1964年，年僅19歲的謝侯開始在專業劇場導戲。<ref name="NYT">{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/08/arts/patrice-chereau-opera-stage-and-film-director-dies-at-68.html | title = Patrice Chéreau, Opera, Stage and Film Director, Dies at 68 | first = Allan | last = Kozinn | authorlink = Allan Kozinn | newspaper = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date = 7 October 2013 | accessdate = 8 October 2013 | archive-date = 2016-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310141242/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/08/arts/patrice-chereau-opera-stage-and-film-director-dies-at-68.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>他曾就讀於[[巴黎大學|巴黎大學]]，並持續在學校進行劇場工作，不過很快便休學。<ref name="Telegraph">{{cite news | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/10365020/Patrice-Chereau.html | type = obituary | title = Patrice Chéreau | newspaper = [[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] | location = London | date = 8 October 2013 | accessdate = 11 October 2013 | archive-date = 2016-03-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160317045128/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/10365020/Patrice-Chereau.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

1994年，他執導的《[[瑪歌皇后_(電影)|瑪歌皇后]]》獲得[[坎城影展評審團獎|坎城影展評審團獎]]；2001年，他前往英國拍攝的《{{link-en|親密關係 (2001年電影)|Intimacy (film)|親密關係}}》則獲得[[柏林影展|柏林影展]][[金熊獎|金熊獎]]；2003年，他以《{{link-fr|死亡詩篇|Son frère}}》再於柏林影展獲得[[最佳導演銀熊獎|最佳導演銀熊獎]]，同年他也擔任[[坎城影展|第56屆坎城影展]][[坎城影展評審團主席名單|評審團主席]]。

2013年10月7日，他因肺癌病逝，享壽68歲。

== 私人生活 ==
巴提斯·謝侯與男演員{{link-fr|帕斯卡尔·格雷戈里|Pascal Greggory}}交往很長的時間，直至謝侯過世<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.theguardian.com/stage/2011/apr/25/patrice-chereau-director-interview-theatre | title = Patrice Chéreau: 'It's OK to be hated' | last = Moss | first = Stephen | work = The Guardian | location = London | date = 25 April 2011 | accessdate = 8 October 2013 | archive-date = 2015-12-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151227125824/http://www.theguardian.com/stage/2011/apr/25/patrice-chereau-director-interview-theatre | dead-url = no }}</ref>；謝侯本人曾表示他對於同性戀主題並不特別有興趣，他認為真正好的故事才能受到大家喜愛，不必侷限於同志題材。<ref name="Independent" />

